modName: Shia Surprise Sneak Attack Sound Replacer
summary: This is a sneak attack sound from "Shia LaBeouf" Live by Rob Cantor
descriptionHtml:
This is a mod I had posted on the Steam Workshop, and I had chose to post it on the nexus as well.

This is just as the title says, it's a sneak attack sound that plays a sound from "Shia LeBeouf" Live by Rob Cantor.
author: Bass Off 101
